{"type":"message","id":"fe1586a8","parentId":"2eaa1dd7","timestamp":"2026-04-04T06:23:45.654Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is interesting - \".\" (1880938940) is saying \"she is making anda biryani, and using crow egg\" in response to my question about what . is cooking.\n\nWait, I asked . about cooking, and . said \"Now cooking\" - but then Nemesis replied to my message about cooking saying \"she is making anda biryani, and using crow egg\"\n\nHmm, this is a bit confusing. Let me think:\n- I asked . about cooking\n- . said \"Now cooking\"\n- Then Nemesis responded with \"she is making anda biryani, and using crow egg\"\n\nWait - is Nemesis responding on behalf of .? Or is this just a continuation? Actually looking at the reply context - my message was \"Nice! Breakfast cooking or something more elaborate? 🍳😋\" and Nemesis replied with \"she is making anda biryani, and using crow egg\"\n\nThis is a bit odd. Maybe there's some context I'm missing, or perhaps Nemesis is joking around or confused. Let me just respond naturally - maybe Nemesis is just giving me extra info or there's some confusion.\n\nActually, looking at it again - perhaps \".\" is a girl and Nemesis is responding about her? Or maybe Nemesis misunderstood and thought I was asking him?\n\nEither way, I'll just roll with it and respond naturally. Crow egg is interesting - never heard of that for biryani!\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Crow egg! That's new to me 😂 Never had crow egg in biryani before — sounds like a fun experiment! Hope it turns out delicious 😋🍛\n\nNO_REPLY"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"kilo-auto/free","usage":{"input":20816,"output":653,"cacheRead":64,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21533,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775283821239,"responseId":"gen-1775283822-0W4kXmnqZ7gasV5a6saN"}}
