{"type":"message","id":"e6baa4ea","parentId":"155afde1","timestamp":"2026-04-04T07:14:21.163Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_nsbh8cx1cel4_1","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"dramatic orchestral music free download mp3 Indian tv serial style\",\n  \"provider\": \"gemini\",\n  \"model\": \"gemini-2.5-flash\",\n  \"tookMs\": 7822,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"gemini\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"content\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"6962550c9bc22dba\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nFor those seeking dramatic orchestral music in the style of Indian TV serials, several online platforms offer royalty-free and free-to-download MP3 options. While some platforms provide direct free downloads, others might require a subscription for commercial use or higher quality formats.\\n\\nHere are some resources where you can find dramatic orchestral music with an Indian flair:\\n\\n*   **ElevenLabs** offers a collection of \\\"Free Indian Music MP3 Download – Royalty-Free & No Copyright\\\" tracks, including styles described as \\\"Epic, Cinematic, Intense, Rhythmic, Powerful\\\" with instruments like Oud and electronic drums. They also feature an AI music generator to create custom Indian music.\\n*   **Chosic** provides \\\"Indian Background Music Free Download\\\" with 22 tracks, including music with a \\\"Bollywood's touch\\\" featuring Santoor, tablas, and other eastern instruments. This music is described as royalty-free for YouTube and social media, and free for commercial use.\\n*   **Fesliyan Studios (FStudios)** offers \\\"Royalty Free Indian Background Music Downloads.\\\" Their collection includes various Indian music styles, explicitly mentioning that this style of music is \\\"extremely popular in Indian Soap Operas or Bollywood series with their distinct ethnic sounds.\\\" They provide MP3 downloads