{"type":"message","id":"110da309","parentId":"05017f60","timestamp":"2026-04-04T07:17:23.525Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_vz3530pviy6g_1","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"free Indian love song mp3 download similar to Jab We Met style\",\n  \"provider\": \"gemini\",\n  \"model\": \"gemini-2.5-flash\",\n  \"tookMs\": 13610,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"gemini\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"content\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"73ea1e2488ae80b2\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nIf you're looking for Indian love songs with a similar feel to the Bollywood hit *Jab We Met*, you're likely drawn to tracks that are romantic, often upbeat, and deeply emotional. The film itself features a popular soundtrack with several beloved love songs.\\n\\n### Songs from \\\"Jab We Met\\\" (2007)\\n\\nThe soundtrack of *Jab We Met* offers a blend of soulful melodies and lively romantic tunes. Some of the standout love songs from the movie include:\\n\\n*   **\\\"Tum Se Hi\\\"** by Mohit Chauhan: This song is a fan favorite, perfectly encapsulating the joy of being in love.\\n*   **\\\"Yeh Ishq Hai\\\"** by Shreya Ghoshal: An energetic track that captures the film's vibrant and romantic spirit.\\n*   **\\\"Aao Meelon Chalein\\\"** by Shaan and Ustad Sultan Khan: A beautiful, melodious song about companionship and journeys.\\n*   **\\\"Nagada Nagada\\\"** by Sonu Nigam and Javed Ali: A festive song with underlying romantic tones.\\n*   **\\\"Aaoge Jab Tum\\\"** by Rashid Khan: A soulful and classical-inspired track that conveys longing and anticipation.\\n\\n### Similar Indian Love Songs\\n\\nFor more songs that evoke a similar romantic and feel-good vibe, consider these Bollywood tracks:\\n\\n*   **\\\"Aaj Din Chadheya\\\"** from *Love Aaj Kal* (2009) by Rahat Fateh Ali Khan: Known for its heartfelt and sincere romantic lyrics.\\n*   **\\\"Haule Haule\\\"** from *Rab Ne Bana Di Jodi* (2008) by Sukhwinder Singh: A sweet song that portrays the subtle beginnings of romance.\\n*   **\\\"Iktara\\\"** from *Wake Up Sid* (2009) by Kavita Seth and Amitabh Bhattacharya: A soulful and reflective song about finding connection.\\n*   **\\\"Khuda Jaane\\\"** from *Bachna Ae Haseeno* (2008) by KK and Shilpa Rao: A grand and popular romantic duet.\\n*   **\\\"Dil Kyun Yeh Mera\\\"** from *Kites* (2010) by KK: A beautiful, slightly melancholic love song.\\n*   **\\\"Bahara\\\"** from *I Hate Luv Storys* (2010) by Shreya Ghoshal and Sona Mohapatra: A cheerful and romantic track.\\n*   **\\\"Tum Hi Ho\\\"** from *Aashiqui 2* (2013) by Arijit Singh: A hugely popular and deeply emotional ballad.\\n*   **\\\"Ranjha\\\"** from *Shershaah* (2021) by B Praak & Jasleen Royal: A more recent song that beautifully captures profound love and longing.\\n*   **\\\"Mast Magan\\\"** from *2 States* (2014) by Arijit Singh & Chinmayi Sripada: A delightful and affectionate love song.\\n*   **\\\"Jashn-E-Bahaaraa\\\"** from *Jodhaa Akbar* (2008) by Javed Ali: A classic, regal romantic song with exquisite lyrics.\\n*   **\\\"Ajab Si\\\"** from *Om Shanti Om* (2007) by KK: An upbeat and charming song about new love.\\n\\n### How to Access These Songs Legally\\n\\nWhile the request is for \\\"free MP3 download,\\\" it's important to note that direct free MP3 downloads for copyrighted music are generally not legal. However, there are several legitimate ways to enjoy these songs:\\n\\n*   **Streaming Services:** Platforms like Gaana, JioSaavn, Spotify, Apple Music, and YouTube Music offer extensive libraries of Indian music, including all the songs listed above. Many provide free tiers with advertisements or premium subscriptions for ad-free listening and downloads for offline playback. Gaana, for example, allows you to stream and download \\\"Jab We Met\\\" MP3 songs through its app.\\n*   **YouTube:** Official music labels often upload songs and music videos to YouTube, where you can listen to them for free.\\n*   **Purchasing Music:** You can legally purchase MP3s or entire albums from online music stores such as Amazon Music or iTunes.\\n\\nThese methods allow you to enjoy your favorite Indian love songs while supporting the artists and creators.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"73ea1e2488ae80b2\\\">>>\",\n  \"citations\": [\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://songspk.com.se/fileslist/2006/jab-we-met-2007/new2old/1.html\",\n      \"title\": \"songspk.com.se\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.thezappybox.com/blogs/news/top-100-evergreen-hindi-romantic-songs\",\n      \"title\": \"thezappybox.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://discover.hubpages.com/entertainment/Hindi-Romantic-Songs-Top-100-Best-Love-Songs-Ever\",\n      \"title\": \"hubpages.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.quora.com/What-songs-would-you-have-on-your-playlist-if-you-like-soothing-Bollywood-songs\",\n      \"title\": \"quora.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://gaana.com/album/jab-we-met\",\n      \"title\": \"gaana.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://gaana.com/album/jab-we-met-hindi\",\n      \"title\": \"gaana.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://gaana.com/playlist/anjanidevi-jab-we-met\",\n      \"title\": \"gaana.com\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"free Indian love song mp3 download similar to Jab We Met style","provider":"gemini","model":"gemini-2.5-flash","tookMs":13610,"externalContent":{"untrusted":true,"source":"web_search","provider":"gemini","wrapped":true},"content":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"73ea1e2488ae80b2\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nIf you're looking for Indian love songs with a similar feel to the Bollywood hit *Jab We Met*, you're likely drawn to tracks that are romantic, often upbeat, and deeply emotional. The film itself features a popular soundtrack with several beloved love songs.\n\n### Songs from \"Jab We Met\" (2007)\n\nThe soundtrack of *Jab We Met* offers a blend of soulful melodies and lively romantic tunes. Some of the standout love songs from the movie include:\n\n*   **\"Tum Se Hi\"** by Mohit Chauhan: This song is a fan favorite, perfectly encapsulating the joy of being in love.\n*   **\"Yeh Ishq Hai\"** by Shreya Ghoshal: An energetic track that captures the film's vibrant and romantic spirit.\n*   **\"Aao Meelon Chalein\"** by Shaan and Ustad Sultan Khan: A beautiful, melodious song about companionship and journeys.\n*   **\"Nagada Nagada\"** by Sonu Nigam and Javed Ali: A festive song with underlying romantic tones.\n*   **\"Aaoge Jab Tum\"** by Rashid Khan: A soulful and classical-inspired track that conveys longing and anticipation.\n\n### Similar Indian Love Songs\n\nFor more songs that evoke a similar romantic and feel-good vibe, consider these Bollywood tracks:\n\n*   **\"Aaj Din Chadheya\"** from *Love Aaj Kal* (2009) by Rahat Fateh Ali Khan: Known for its heartfelt and sincere romantic lyrics.\n*   **\"Haule Haule\"** from *Rab Ne Bana Di Jodi* (2008) by Sukhwinder Singh: A sweet song that portrays the subtle beginnings of romance.\n*   **\"Iktara\"** from *Wake Up Sid* (2009) by Kavita Seth and Amitabh Bhattacharya: A soulful and reflective song about finding connection.\n*   **\"Khuda Jaane\"** from *Bachna Ae Haseeno* (2008) by KK and Shilpa Rao: A grand and popular romantic duet.\n*   **\"Dil Kyun Yeh Mera\"** from *Kites* (2010) by KK: A beautiful, slightly melancholic love song.\n*   **\"Bahara\"** from *I Hate Luv Storys* (2010) by Shreya Ghoshal and Sona Mohapatra: A cheerful and romantic track.\n*   **\"Tum Hi Ho\"** from *Aashiqui 2* (2013) by Arijit Singh: A hugely popular and deeply emotional ballad.\n*   **\"Ranjha\"** from *Shershaah* (2021) by B Praak & Jasleen Royal: A more recent song that beautifully captures profound love and longing.\n*   **\"Mast Magan\"** from *2 States* (2014) by Arijit Singh & Chinmayi Sripada: A delightful and affectionate love song.\n*   **\"Jashn-E-Bahaaraa\"** from *Jodhaa Akbar* (2008) by Javed Ali: A classic, regal romantic song with exquisite lyrics.\n*   **\"Ajab Si\"** from *Om Shanti Om* (2007) by KK: An upbeat and charming song about new love.\n\n### How to Access These Songs Legally\n\nWhile the request is for \"free MP3 download,\" it's important to note that direct free MP3 downloads for copyrighted music are generally not legal. However, there are several legitimate ways to enjoy these songs:\n\n*   **Streaming Services:** Platforms like Gaana, JioSaavn, Spotify, Apple Music, and YouTube Music offer extensive libraries of Indian music, including all the songs listed above. Many provide free tiers with advertisements or premium subscriptions for ad-free listening and downloads for offline playback. Gaana, for example, allows you to stream and download \"Jab We Met\" MP3 songs through its app.\n*   **YouTube:** Official music labels often upload songs and music videos to YouTube, where you can listen to them for free.\n*   **Purchasing Music:** You can legally purchase MP3s or entire albums from online music stores such as Amazon Music or iTunes.\n\nThese methods allow you to enjoy your favorite Indian love songs while supporting the artists and creators.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"73ea1e2488ae80b2\">>>","citations":[{"url":"https://songspk.com.se/fileslist/2006/jab-we-met-2007/new2old/1.html","title":"songspk.com.se"},{"url":"https://www.thezappybox.com/blogs/news/top-100-evergreen-hindi-romantic-songs","title":"thezappybox.com"},{"url":"https://discover.hubpages.com/entertainment/Hindi-Romantic-Songs-Top-100-Best-Love-Songs-Ever","title":"hubpages.com"},{"url":"https://www.quora.com/What-songs-would-you-have-on-your-playlist-if-you-like-soothing-Bollywood-songs","title":"quora.com"},{"url":"https://gaana.com/album/jab-we-met","title":"gaana.com"},{"url":"https://gaana.com/album/jab-we-met-hindi","title":"gaana.com"},{"url":"