{"type":"message","id":"bf7af009","parentId":"71684034","timestamp":"2026-04-04T08:50:55.220Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Sravya is asking for games like Temple Run, Ludo etc. These are mobile games - I can't actually run Temple Run or Ludo on this server! Those are mobile games you'd play on a phone.\n\nI should clarify this and maybe suggest some text-based games we CAN play in the chat, or see if there's something else we can do.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Haha — Temple Run & Ludo are mobile games! I'd need *your* phone to play those, not my server! 😅\n\n**But We CAN play in chat:**\n\n🎲 **20 Questions** — I think of something, you guess!\n🧩 **Brain Teaser** — I post a riddle, group guesses!\n🎯 **This or That** — I give two options, you pick!\n📝 **Word Association** — I say word, you say first thing that comes to mind!\n😏 **Truth or Dare** — Classic!\n\nOr if you want actual mobile game recommendations — what's YOUR go-to? 🎮\n\nLet's play one now? 😄🖤"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"kilo-auto/free","usage":{"input":400,"output":295,"cacheRead":69184,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69879,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775292646477,"responseId":"gen-1775292647-bbuDneJjxox77r1itQiN"}}
