{"type":"message","id":"4daf7b62","parentId":"a7064778","timestamp":"2026-04-04T08:53:45.276Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about video games - probably recommendations for PlayStation games. Let me give some solid recommendations!\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Ah YOU want game recommendations! 🎮 Here are MUST-PLAYs:\n\n**PS5 Exclusives:**\n- 🎯 **Spider-Man 2** — Best web-slinging action!\n- ⚔️ **God of War Ragnarök** — Epic Norse mythology\n- 🧊 **Final Fantasy XVI** — Incredible story\n- 🎃 **Astro's Playroom** — Free, adorable!\n\n**PS5/PS4 Cross:**\n- 🧟 **The Last of Us Part I & II** — Emotional horror\n- 🏎️ **Gran Turismo 7** — Stunning racing\n- ⚽ **FC 25** — Football perfection!\n\n**Co-op/Party:**\n- 🎮 **It Takes Two** — MUST play with a friend!\n- 🏰 **Castle Crashers** — Classic beat 'em up\n\n**What's YOUR vibe?**\n- 🎬 Story-driven?\n- ⚔️ Action/Combat?\n- 🏃 Platformer?\n- 🧩 Puzzles?\n\nTell me what you like and I'll tailor! 😄🖤"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"kilo-auto/free","usage":{"input":609,"output":281,"cacheRead":70064,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":70954,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775292815932,"responseId":"gen-1775292816-A80vb5YdR4lYjKir0SrU"}}
