{"type":"message","id":"d1bfbcf5","parentId":"d5e629d5","timestamp":"2026-04-04T08:54:40.009Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Sravya likes horror games! Let me give her some good horror game recommendations for PlayStation.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Ah, horror lover! 👻 Here's YOUR list:\n\n**PS5/PS4 Must-Play Horror:**\n\n🔪 **The Last of Us Part I & II** — Emotional + intense horror. Masterpiece.\n\n🧟 **Resident Evil Village (RE8)** — Vampire ladies, terrifying dungeons! Gold.\n\n🦇 **Resident Evil 4 Remake** — Modern classic. Perfect balance.\n\n🌙 **Silent Hill 2 Remake** — Psychological horror legend. Deeply unsettling.\n\n👁️ **Layers of Fear** — Mind-bending psychological\n\n🪟 **Alan Wake 2** — Meta, supernatural, gripping story!\n\n**For quick hits:**\n- ⏱️ **Phasmophobia** — Co-op ghost hunting! (PS5 soon)\n\n**Vibe check:**\n- 🎬 Story-heavy? → Alan Wake 2, Last of Us\n- 🔪 Action-survival? → RE Village, RE4\n- 🧠 Psychological? → Silent Hill 2, Layers of Fear\n- 👫 With friends? → Phasmophobia, Dead by Daylight\n\n**START HERE:** If you haven't → \"The Last of Us Part I\" 🔥\n\nWhat's YOUR pick? 😱🖤"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"kilo-auto/free","usage":{"input":663,"output":302,"cacheRead":70656,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":71621,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775292868750,"responseId":"gen-1775292869-RSmJuDNmd7qLs5zgn87J"}}
