{"type":"message","id":"4c02d388","parentId":"12a1e94c","timestamp":"2026-04-04T08:56:49.275Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking whether these games are video games or specifically for PlayStation. They might be confused and thinking these are PlayStation-specific games.\n\nLet me clarify - all of these are VIDEO GAMES that can be played on PLAYSTATION (PS4/PS5). Most are also available on PC, Xbox, etc.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"All of these are **VIDEO GAMES** 🎮\n\nAnd they run on **PlayStation** (PS4/PS5) — that's why I recommended them!\n\n**Where to play:**\n| Game | PS4 | PS5 | PC | Xbox |\n|------|-----|------|-----|------|\n| The Last of Us | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ |\n| RE Village | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |\n| RE4 Remake | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |\n| Silent Hill 2 | ❌ | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |\n| Alan Wake 2 | ❌ | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |\n\n**Key:**\n- ✅ = Available\n- ❌ = Not available\n\nSo you need a **PlayStation** (or PC/Xbox) to play these!\n\n**PS5 recommendation:** Best for horror — DualSense haptic feedback makes it SO much more intense! 🎯\n\nAnything else I can clear up? 😄"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"kilo-auto/free","usage":{"input":886,"output":344,"cacheRead":72032,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73262,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775293003142,"responseId":"gen-1775293003-DcbARvz0VoRJz3PbY9DB"}}
