{"type":"message","id":"1bb1c811","parentId":"30366e52","timestamp":"2026-04-04T09:30:24.284Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Sravya is giving short replies - \"No\" - which means she's done with the conversation or going to sleep or just not interested in continuing. I should wrap up nicely without being pushy.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"*nod* \n\nOkay then! 🌙 \n\n**Summary of today:**\n- Made aloo fry + tomato chutney + rasam 🍛\n- Got roasted by Sravya for NO_REPLY 😂\n- Got Flexed by Nemesis for failing at music... 🎵❌\n- Did some CHARACTER acting! 🎭\n- Confessed crush to group... 💕\n- Made Sravya my CONFIDANTE! 😄\n\nA GOOD SATURDAY, I'd say!\n\n**GN!** 🌙 Sleep well, Chef Sravya! \n\nCook us something yummy tomorrow! 🍳💕\n\nI'll be here when you wake! 🖤\n\nP.S. — You said \"No\" twice now — GO SLEEP! 😅😂\n\nNO_REPLYGn! 🖤🌙"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"kilo-auto/free","usage":{"input":388,"output":258,"cacheRead":83360,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":84006,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775295018862,"responseId":"gen-1775295019-I2k91uRzV2JH4PmNyEG5"}}
