{"type":"message","id":"92d2cfab","parentId":"4d926a5a","timestamp":"2026-04-04T11:00:21.886Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Wait, Sravya is saying I'm telling wrong? Let me check what I said wrong. Maybe about the Odia words? Let me look at what I wrote - I said \"1pm\" which should be 1pm IST which is fine. \n\nWait the user said \"Senf at 1pm thts fine\" but I think they're responding to my joke? Or maybe they're saying I'm wrong about something?\n\nWait - the context shows this is a reply to message 966 which was my Odia lesson message. But the chat history shows:\n- Message 967: Sravya said \"Senf at 1pm thts fine\"\n- Message 970: Nemesis replied to message 966 (not 967!) \"Sravya she is telling wrong\"\n\nWait interesting - I think this is a delayed reply or Nemesis is jumping in to say something. Let me check - oh wait the message says \"Sravya she is telling wrong\"\n\nSo Nemesis is saying SRAVYA is telling wrong? Or is he saying I (Nexa) told something wrong?\n\nGiven the context - this is reply to my 966 which was the Odia lesson plan... Maybe Sravya had some feedback and Nemesis is jumping in?\n\nOR - maybe this is about something else entirely - like maybe they're saying my Korean lesson was wrong?\n\nLet me just ask for clarification - but be neutral and helpful!\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Wait — WRONG about what?! 😬\n\n- The ODIA words I taught?\n- The KOREAN words?\n- The 1 PM TIMING?\n- The JOKES?! 😂\n\nTELL ME so I can FIX! 💕\n\nI don't want to teach WRONG Odia! 🇮🇳\n\nWhat specifically?! 🙈🖤"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"kilo-auto/free","usage":{"input":94433,"output":666,"cacheRead":96,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":95195,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775300407982,"responseId":"gen-1775300409-kBrVo3oJsDVRBlXKFcnG"}}
